Refdeɣ-t yujjaq, serseɣ-t yujjaq, amek ara sxedmeɣ ay axellaq!
Ǧǧiɣ lwiz yemmenṭar, ula win as-yegan leqrar.
Yekkes-d afus i tsebbalt.
Ad ak-d-yerr adrar d luḍa.
Tissirt ma tuɣ-itent deg rryac, ula i as-d-xedmen iɣuraf.
Awackan i d-yegga ufus-im, mačči aweckan i d-tegga tnuḍt-im.
Qerrceɣ-am egg awackan i yinebgi i am-d-ikecmen.
Meyyez qbel aneggez.
Awal am terṣṣaṣt.
Awal yeqsed win yeɛna, tarṣaṣt teqsed win tenɣa.
Talaba, teɛǧeb win i tt-yersan mačči d win i tt-yeẓḍan.
Ulac win yellan akken yebɣa, nteddu akken nufa.
Talaba almend uḍar-ik.
Tiṭ-is d aɛeqqa n uzemmur yewwan, laɛyun-is d lxiḍ n uzegza yeɣman.
Yenna-as: "A nnbi ḥemmleɣ-k." Yerra-as: "Seqsi ul-ik ad ak-yemmel."
Ssɛaya d anyir, ṣṣaba d awzir.
Tabaqit n lmerǧan ur keččmen yizan.
Ṣṣyada, ṣbaḥ i tt-ferqen; aḥlil i yimeɣban yeṭṭsen.
Alɣem yettwali kan taɛrurt n gma-s, taɛrurt-is ur tt-yettwali ara.
zuɣer icifaḍ ar tafeḍ isebbaḍen.
